document_data.name: Keskrel
document_data.mainbody: '''House Keskrel''' was one of the noble families of [[Cormyr]]. House Keskrel was one of the oldest noble families of [[Marsember]], although a minor one.{{Cite dragon/412/Eye on the Realms: The Thing in the Crypt}}
document_data.History: House Keskrel were known for they loyalty to House [[Obarskyr]], and were ennobled because of their martial prowess.
document_data.Members: * [[Rordurn Keskrel]] was the first of the Keskrel lords.
